OL,3,CMan, 28, set to appear in court
OL,4,Ccharged with murder of Ann Widdecombe
OL,6,FA 28-year-old man is set to appear in
OL,7,Fcourt charged with the murder of
OL,8,Fformer MP Ann Widdecombe.
OL,10,FJoshua Kerry, from Rotherham, South
OL,11,FYorkshire, is due to appear at
OL,12,FWestminster Magistrates' Court on
OL,13,FTuesday morning charged with the
OL,14,Fmurder of the Reform UK spokeswoman.
OL,16,FKerry, who has been remanded into
OL,17,Fcustody, was first arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of murder on July 11, two
OL,19,Fdays after the 78-year-old was found
OL,20,Fdead at her home in Devon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
