PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784607479
OL,3,CMan, 28, set to appear in court
OL,4,Ccharged with murder of Ann Widdecombe
OL,6,FTwo days after he was arrested for
OL,7,Fmurder, Kerry was additionally
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of the
OL,9,Fcommission, preparation or instigation
OL,10,Fof acts of terrorism, but he has not
OL,11,Fbeen charged with this offence.
OL,13,FFrank Ferguson, Chief Crown Prosecutor
OL,14,Fof the CPS Special Crime and Counter
OL,15,FTerrorism Division, said: "We have
OL,16,Fdecided to prosecute Joshua Kerry for
OL,17,Fmurder following a police
OL,18,Finvestigation into the death of Ann
OL,19,FWiddecombe in Haytor, Dartmoor.
OL,26,@wD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
