PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784607479
OL,3,CMan, 28, set to appear in court
OL,4,Ccharged with murder of Ann Widdecombe
OL,6,F"Police inquiries into the defendant's
OL,7,Fmotives are ongoing, including a
OL,8,Fpotential political or terrorist
OL,9,Fconnection.
OL,11,F"Our prosecutors have worked closely
OL,12,Fwith the police to establish that
OL,13,Fthere is sufficient evidence to bring
OL,14,Fthis case to court, and we will
OL,15,Fcontinue working with them as their
OL,16,Finvestigation progresses."
