OL,3,CMan, 28, set to appear in court
OL,4,Ccharged with murder of Ann Widdecombe
OL,6,FMiss Widdecombe was first elected as a
OL,7,FConservative MP in Kent in 1987, and
OL,8,Fwent on to become an MEP for the
OL,9,FBrexit Party and then a spokeswoman
OL,10,Ffor Reform UK.
OL,12,FShe also found fame outside politics
OL,13,Fafter starring in Strictly Come
OL,14,FDancing and Celebrity Big Brother.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
