PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784607479
OL,3,CMan, 28, set to appear in court
OL,4,Ccharged with murder of Ann Widdecombe
OL,6,FPrime Minister Andy Burnham called for
OL,7,Fa serious review of MPs' safety after
OL,8,FMiss Widdecombe's death and head of UK
OL,9,FCounter Terrorism Policing Laurence
OL,10,FTaylor said officers are working with
OL,11,Fparliamentary officials to make
OL,12,Fpoliticians aware of protection
OL,13,Fmeasures that are in place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
