PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784607479
OL,3,CMan, 28, set to appear in court
OL,4,Ccharged with murder of Ann Widdecombe
OL,6,FSpeaking outside New Scotland Yard on
OL,7,FMonday, Mr Taylor said: "I know many
OL,8,Fhave been understandably concerned
OL,9,Fabout their own safety after this
OL,10,Fhorrendous attack, particularly after
OL,11,Fhearing about the nature of the attack
OL,12,Fshe (Miss Widdecombe) endured in her
OL,13,Fown home.
OL,15,F"We are working closely with the
OL,16,FSpeaker of the House and the relevant
OL,17,Fauthorities to ensure elected
OL,18,Fofficials are aware of what we have in
OL,19,Fplace to protect them."
